{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3e795d4b3f","title":"控制妙香山小白山隔断东西两敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fa8997dc81","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":21,"articleId":"3e795d4b3f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"713da38a94","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭、邓，指彭德怀、邓华，当时分别任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员和第十三兵团司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"62e01d2427","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"妙香山，位于慈江道、平安北道、平安南道交界处。小白山，属狼林山脉，位于慈江道、平安南道交界处。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4db94a7efe","type":"title","text":"控制妙香山小白山隔断东西两敌","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f"},{"id":"713da38a94","type":"subtitle","text":"彭、邓“：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f"},{"id":"62e01d2427","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）请注意控制平安南、平安北、咸镜三道交界之妙香山、小白山等制高点，隔断东西两敌，勿让敌人占去为要。（二）敌人测向颜准，请加注意。（三）熙川或其他适当地点应速筑可靠的防空洞，保障你们司令部的安全","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f"},{"id":"01c43ffc3c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f"},{"id":"00ca3da727","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十一日四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f"}],"page":{"id":"27a0792758","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3e795d4b3f","start":264,"end":264}}}},"__N_SSG":true}